-- Linc Energy CEO Says Australia Should Scrap Mining Tax
-- B y
-- 2013-09-06T21:04:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-09-06/linc-energy-ceo-says-australia-should-scrap-mining-tax-video-.html
Peter Bond, chief executive officer 
of Linc Energy Ltd., an Australian company that is developing a 
technology known as underground coal gasification, talks about 
the Sept. 7 federal election and its potential implications for 
the  mining industry .  Bond also talks about the company's business strategy. He 
speaks from Brisbane with Susan Li on Bloomberg Television's 
"First Up." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 07:26
 